summary: Highly motivated, creative Master of Science with extremely strong organizational, interpersonal and communication skills including Dutch fluency, moderate French and Spanish fluency and German language skills. Demonstrated ability to work independently to manage and prioritize multiple tasks with strong attention to detail, flexibility to meet and adapt to changes in organizational priorities. Highly analytical with the ability to think strategically, learn quickly and master new concepts. Determined, ambitious and reliable team player with a positive attitude.
